</p>
						
						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/South-African-GM-label-confusion" title="South African GM label confusion" alt="link">South African GM label confusion</a></h2>

	
					<p>  Nature, 06 March 2006, Most maize and soy products sold in South African food stores contain detectable amounts of genetically modified organisms (GMOs), including products that are labeled 'non-GMO,' 'GMO-free,' or 'organic,' reveals a study by the University of the Free State in Bloemfontein in South Africa. </p>
							<p><span class="date">10/03/2006</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/South-African-GM-label-confusion">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
</div>
</p>
						
						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Technology-centre-to-be-established-in-Patterson-name" title="Technology centre to be established in Patterson' name " alt="link">Technology centre to be established in Patterson' name </a></h2>

	
					<p> Jamaica Gleaner News, 18 Feburary 2006, Jamaica will soon have a regional science and technology centre that will be named for Prime Minister PJ Patterson The institute will offer a high-level course for senior public officials and private sector leaders on science and technology innovation.</p>
							<p><span class="date">10/03/2006</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Technology-centre-to-be-established-in-Patterson-name">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
</div>
</p>
